Package ca.on.oicr.gsi.shesmu.plugin.types

Class ReturnTypeGuarantee<T>

java.lang.Object
ca.on.oicr.gsi.shesmu.plugin.types.GenericReturnTypeGuarantee<T>
ca.on.oicr.gsi.shesmu.plugin.types.ReturnTypeGuarantee<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the Java type being exported to Shesmu
public abstract class ReturnTypeGuarantee<T> extends GenericReturnTypeGuarantee<T>
Matches to make Java's type checking produce correct types in Shesmu

This class doesn't do anything per-se, it just allows Java type checker to produce a type that is compatible with a Shesmu Imyhat without much work on the part of the author
